com.tibco.tea.agent.support

Class TeaIllegalStateException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • java.lang.RuntimeException
          • com.tibco.tea.agent.support.TeaException
            • com.tibco.tea.agent.support.TeaIllegalStateException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class TeaIllegalStateException
extends TeaException
    Exception to indicate a conflict between the TeaOperation intent and the current state of the object on which the TeaOperation was invoked. The object state should not change when this exception is thrown.The HTTP status code used for indicating this exception is 409.
    See Also:
